  Sensors --> SO
  SPL --> QP
  QP --> SO
  SO --> WMS
  WMS --> PROJ

  APL --> CP
  CP --> SKO
  SKO --> ASE
  ASE --> REP
  ASE --> Actuators

  O -- "EvidenceFrame<br>what evidence matters?" --> QP
  PROJ -- "OperationalEvidence" --> A

  O -- "ExecutionContract<br>what skill should run?" --> CP
